title: Women's adidas Originals NMD_Racer Primeknit Shoes
description: Channeling the streamlined look of an '80s racer, these shoes are updated with modern features. The foot-hugging adidas Primeknit upper offers a soft, breathable feel. The Boost midsole provides responsive comfort accented with a contrast-color EVA heel plug. Embroidered details add a distinctive finish.

title: Women's adidas Originals Sleek Shoes
description: A modern take on adidas sport heritage, tailored just for women. Perforated 3-Stripes on the leather upper of these shoes offer a sleek look that mirrors iconic tennis styles.

title: Women's adidas Swim Puka Slippers
description: These adidas Puka slippers for women's come with slim straps for a great fit. Feature performance logo on the footbed and textured Rubber outsole that gives unique comfort.

title: Women's adidas Sport Inspired Questar Ride Shoes
description: Inspired by modern tech runners, these women's shoes step out with unexpected style. They're built with a breathable knit upper, while the heel offers the extra support of an Achilles-hugging design. The cushioned midsole provides a soft landing with every stride.

title: Women's adidas Originals Taekwondo Shoes
description: This design is inspired by vintage Taekwondo styles originally worn to perfect high kicks and rapid foot strikes. The canvas shoes make a streetwear fashion statement as a chic, foot-hugging slip-on. They're shaped for a narrow, women's-specific fit and ride on a soft gum rubber outsole.

title: Women's adidas Sport Inspired Duramo Lite 2.0 Shoes
description: Refine your interval training in these women's versatile running-inspired shoes. Featuring a lightweight mesh and synthetic upper, they combine responsive midsole cushioning with a soft collar that reduces ankle pressure.

title: WOMEN'S ADIDAS RUNNING DURAMO 9 SHOES
description: These women's neutral running shoes will get you on the road to your goals. A sandwich mesh upper offers lightweight breathability, while a seamless print overlay adds support for a stable stride. The midsole offers pillow-soft Cloudfoam cushioning that eases every stride.

title: Women's adidas Originals Forest Grove Shoes
description: The Forest Grove brings back the look of the adidas Oregon running design from the '80s. A favourite for marathon training, it had a distinctive look and feel with shock-absorbing cushioning and a web-wrapped midsole. These streetwear shoes echo the original look with a textured nubuck and mesh upper. A web overlay on the midsole adds authentic Oregon style.

title: Women's adidas Originals Swift Run Shoes
description: The Swift distills decades of adidas heritage running designs. Made for casual everyday wear, these lightweight knit shoes come with a sleek shape and a supportive yet flexible feel. They stand out with embroidered accents and smooth welded details. An EVA midsole adds all-day wearability.

title: Women's adidas Originals Continental Vulc Shoes
description: These low-profile shoes come in a pastel color for a feminine touch. A mix of nubuck and canvas on the upper adds texture. The suede toe cap is abrasion-resistant so they look fresh and new longer. A vulcanized outsole makes them durable.

title: Women's adidas Running Duramo 9 Shoes
description: These women's neutral running shoes will get you on the road to your goals. A sandwich mesh upper offers lightweight breathability, while a seamless print overlay adds support for a stable stride. The midsole offers pillow-soft Cloudfoam cushioning that eases every stride.

title: Women's adidas Running Duramo 9 Shoes
description: These women's neutral running shoes will get you on the road to your goals. A sandwich mesh upper offers lightweight breathability, while a seamless print overlay adds support for a stable stride. The midsole offers pillow-soft Cloudfoam cushioning that eases every stride.

title: Men's adidas Sport Inspired Response Trail Shoes
description: When the road turns to trail, all that matters is what lies ahead. These running shoes deliver a plush ride and confident grip in a fresh, sporty look. Cloudfoam cushioning feels ultra-soft while the aggressive outsole grabs on in all directions. The multilayer upper and sleek 3-Stripes elevate your look when you get back to town.

title: Men's adidas Sport Inspired Run 70s Shoes
description: These running-inspired shoes are designed with a mesh upper and a textile lining for flexible, all-day comfort. 3-Stripes and a rubber outsole give the shoes a stylish sign-off.

title: Men's adidas Sport Inspired Drogo Shoes
description: The adidas running-inspired shoes for men. An excellent combination of breathable Mesh with synthetic overlays on the upper makes it very comfortable for your feet on the run. Durable and non slippery one piece super grip EVA midsole and outsole ensures maximum stability and grip on the ground.

title: Men's adidas Running Nayo 1.0 shoes
description: The adidas Nayo 1.0 shoes for men. These lightweight running shoes give all round comfort, cushioning, durability & support in a simplistic design. The mesh upper ensure breathability and durability while the Light strike EVA midsole provides premium cushioning's. Full Rubber outsole provides durability.

title: Men's adidas Sports Inspired Lite Racer Shoes
description: The ultra-lightweight build of these shoes takes a running-inspired style to the streets. The sporty look has a breathable and durable mesh upper with stitched-on 3-Stripes. EVA cushioning provides lightweight comfort for every step.

title: Men's adidas Running Nepton 2.0 Shoes
description:
Sleek design with reflective three stripes makes it a contemporary yet functional
shoe. Breathable textile upper for maximum ventilation and a cushioned midsole provides all-day comfort with rubber outsole for best durability in high wear areas.

title: Men's adidas Running Torik Shoes
description: A well cushioned shoe with a fresher look that will appeal to young runners. Features Mesh upper for maximum ventilation, lightstrike IMEVA midsole with visible adiprene providing protection from harmful impact forces and durable Rubber outsole for long-lasting wear.

title: Men's adidas Sport Inspired Kalus 1.0 Shoes
description: A well cushioned running-inspired shoes with a fresher look that will appeal to all. Features Mesh upper for maximum ventilation, lightstrike IMEVA midsole with visible adiprene providing protection from harmful impact forces and durable Rubber outsole for long-lasting wear.

title: Men's adidas Running Duramo 9 Shoes
description: These men's running shoes will get you on the road to your goals. A sandwich mesh upper offers lightweight breathability, while a seamless print overlay adds support for a stable stride. The midsole offers pillow-soft Cloudfoam cushioning that eases every stride.

title: MEN'S adidas  RUNNING YAMO 1.0 SHOES
description: The adidas Yamo 1.0 shoes for men. These lightweight running shoes have a combination of Synthetic with double layer Mesh ensure breathability and durability while the Lightstrike EVA midsole provides premium cushionings. Full Rubber outsole provides durability.

title: Men's ADIDAS RUNNING NEBULAR 1.0 SHOES
description: The premium looking adidas Nebular 1.0 Running shoes for men crafted with Mesh overlays which make it lightweight. The breathable sandwich Mesh offer extended ventilation and comfort. Light strike IMEVA midsole with full Rubber outsole provides durability.

title: MEN'S ADIDAS RUNNING LEGUS SHOES
description: Get maximum support, comfort and a refreshed look with these adidas Legus shoes for men. The textile mesh upper is breathable and has a sock-like fit and the supportive cage in the shoe's midfoot provides midfoot lockdown. CLOUDFOAM gives  instant step in-comfort, long-lasting responsive cushioning and a super-plush feel and the Rubber outsole gives ultimate durability.
